### Genfeed API - Avatars Collection Endpoints
### Read-only endpoints: list avatars, fetch provider voices/avatars
### Avatar video generation -> POST /videos/avatar
### Lip-sync generation   -> POST /videos/lip-sync

########################################
# List & Filter Avatars
########################################

### Get All Avatars (Paginated)
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### Get User Avatars
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars?user={{testUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

########################################
# Provider Voices
########################################

### Get HeyGen Voices
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars/heygen/voices
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### Get Hedra Voices
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars/hedra/voices
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### Get ElevenLabs Voices
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars/elevenlabs/voices
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

########################################
# Provider Avatars
########################################

### Get HeyGen Avatars
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars/heygen/avatars
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### Get Hedra Avatars
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars/hedra/avatars
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Unauthorized Access
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/avatars
